title: Prime Office Space for Rent in the Heart of Ngamwongwan
description: 50, Soi Ngamwongwan 57, Lat Yao Subdistrict, Chatuchak District, Bangkok 10900
promp:
Office space for rent in the heart of Ngamwongwan

Elevate your business with a 9-story office building located in a prime area near The Mall Ngamwongwan and expressway access.

Offering a variety of rental sizes with full facilities to suit different types of businesses.

Project Highlights:

◒ Prime location on Ngamwongwan Road, close to shopping malls and expressway access
◒ 9-story building with passenger elevators
◒ Rental units start from 30 sq.m., suitable for both small and large businesses
◒ Full facilities: parking, security system, air conditioning, and ready-to-use electricity and water systems
◒ Easy access by private car and public transport
dividedOffice: Shared Office Space, 1 Parking Spot per Room
wholeFloorDesc: Full-floor office with over 368 sq.m., starting at 300 / sq.m. (excluding electricity)
